OL,3,CSubsidy card for gluten-free food
OL,4,Claunched in Wales
OL,6,FA new pre-paid card will be rolled out
OL,7,Facross Wales to give people who
OL,8,Freceive gluten-free food on
OL,9,Fprescription greater choice and
OL,10,Ffreedom.
OL,12,FThe gluten-free subsidy card will
OL,13,Fallow people with conditions like
OL,14,Fcoeliac disease and dermatitis
OL,15,Fherpetiformis to access a wider range
OL,16,Fof gluten-free foods in supermarkets
OL,17,Fand online, instead of relying only on
OL,18,Fa prescription.
