OL,3,CSubsidy card for gluten-free food
OL,4,Claunched in Wales
OL,6,FThe scheme is an alternative way for
OL,7,Fpeople to access these foods and will
OL,8,Fbe rolled out across Wales from the
OL,9,Fautumn.
OL,11,FThose who currently receive gluten-
OL,12,Ffree food on prescription will be
OL,13,Fcontacted by their health board once
OL,14,Fthe scheme goes live in their local
OL,15,Farea.
