OL,3,CSubsidy card for gluten-free food
OL,4,Claunched in Wales
OL,6,F"The scheme will contribute to
OL,7,Freducing administrative burdens on GPs
OL,8,Fand pharmacies, while promoting a more
OL,9,Feffective use of NHS resources."
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, the Cabinet
OL,12,FSecretary confirmed that people will
OL,13,Fstill be able to get gluten-free food
OL,14,Fon prescription for free.
