OL,3,CSubsidy card for gluten-free food
OL,4,Claunched in Wales
OL,6,F"This is a choice which we're giving
OL,7,Fto patients. We've had a very
OL,8,Fsuccessful pilot in parts of Wales -
OL,9,Factually patients have really welcomed
OL,10,Fthe flexibility which it brings and
OL,11,Fthe ability to normalise what is
OL,12,Fotherwise something which has been
OL,13,Fmedicalised for people," he added.
OL,15,F"So, I think there's been enthusiasm
OL,16,Famongst patients for the flexibility
OL,17,Fwhich this gives them to choose."
OL,19,FThe new card scheme has been
OL,20,Fextensively tested in Hywel Dda
OL,21,FUniversity Health Board.
