OL,3,CSubsidy card for gluten-free food
OL,4,Claunched in Wales
OL,6,F"The card empowers me to buy the food
OL,7,FI want and make better lifestyle
OL,8,Fchoices. It's one of the best
OL,9,Fcontributors to my healthier life."
OL,11,FDietician Alison Jones, who led the
OL,12,Fsuccessful pilot and implementation at
OL,13,FHywel Dda said she is "delighted" to
OL,14,Fsee the card being adopted across
OL,15,FWales.
